      "description": "Up for sale is a dependable vehicle in good overall condition, making it an excellent choice for a daily driver. The engine is strong and has been consistently maintained, paired with a transmission that shifts smoothly through every gear. While the interior is clean and well-kept, you may notice some minor cosmetic wear on the upholstery and a few light scratches on the exterior, consistent with its age. All electronics and climate control systems are fully functional, and the tires have plenty of tread remaining. This is a solid, honest car that is ready for the road without any immediate repairs needed.",
