    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014it's been well-cared for and is totally ready for its next big adventure with you! Everything runs super smoothly, and it still looks great parked in the driveway. If you\u2019re looking for something reliable, comfy, and fun, this is definitely the one. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home, so come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
