      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained 2018 executive sedan in a striking Deep Sea Blue Metallic finish. This vehicle represents a sophisticated balance of performance and luxury, having been primarily garage-kept and serviced exclusively at authorized centers. The exterior retains a deep, high-gloss luster, though a careful eye will find a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with respectful daily use. Inside, the premium Dakota leather interior remains supple and clean; the cabin is strictly smoke-free and all onboard electronics, including the widescreen navigation and premium surround-sound system, function flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, featuring a complete service log, a very recent oil and filter change, and high-performance tires with approximately 70% tread remaining. It drives straight and true with no unusual noises, offering the smooth, responsive power delivery and tight handling you expect from a premium marque. This is a dependable, high-quality vehicle that has been cared for with an eye for detail, now ready for its next owner.",
